text: Rhodopteriana geita is a moth in the family Eupterotidae. It was described by Philippe Darge in 2013. It is found in Tanzania. 2013c: Nouvelles especes de Rhodopteriana Bouyer, 2012. (Lepidoptera, Eupterotidae). Saturnafrica, 15: 35-42. ==References== Category:Moths described in 2013 Category:Janinae
